{"data":[{"date":"06:41 06/08","title":"M\u1ed9t tay h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t Chelsea, Aguero xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/5-diem-nhan-rut-ra-tu-tran-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-Sieu-Cup-Anh-2018-hinh-anh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rio Ferdinand h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 13 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 v\u00e0 m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec1u cho Man City. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 200 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 7 n\u0103m qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/5-diem-nhan-rut-ra-tu-tran-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-Sieu-Cup-Anh-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea 0-2 Man City n\u00ean hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean, Aguero \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn v\u00f4 v\u00e0n l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u. Sau \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Pep Guardiola th\u00ec t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rio Ferdinand c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Aguero ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Hai ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1eabu c\u00f3 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e2m c\u1ea3nh kh\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd Aguero c\u00f2n hay h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Harry Kane, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n d\u0129 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e0i gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.\u201d \u2013 G\u1ea1t qua t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Man City th\u1eadm ch\u00ed xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-Chelsea-vs-Man-City.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2039","checkdouble":"193805"},{"date":"00:52 06/08","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ASIAD 2018 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine hay Oman kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thay \u0111\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nh\u1ecbp l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 \u00f4ng Lee Young-jin \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0i to\u00e1n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch nghi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AFF Cup. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park Hang-seo. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean U23 kh\u00e1c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 khung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf k\u1ef3 AFF Cup 2018 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m\u201d, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2038","checkdouble":"193807"},{"date":"04:39 06/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/diem-nhan-tran-chelsea-vs-man-cirty-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t:</h2>\r\n<h2>Sergio Aguero\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aguero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 200 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aguero ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-hom-nay-372-193779.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea vs Man City</span> v\u1eeba qua. Anh l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAguero \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Luiz &ndash; Rudiger c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Aguero. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAguero \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng Rudiger \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Luiz \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Aguero c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua David Luiz kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho HLV Pep Guardiola th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thay v\u00ec Gabriel Jesus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bernardo Silva</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Bernardo Silva sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, Silva \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &ldquo; nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng d\u00f9 l\u00e0 nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Bernardo Silva x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva s\u1ebd l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man City m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c De Bruyne v\u00e0 Sterling s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd xoay s\u1edf th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willy Caballero\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willy Caballero\" title=\"Willy Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/033503-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Willy Caballero c\u1ee9u cho Chelsea v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u00f4ng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Cheasea. Sau s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Callum Hudson-Odoi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Caballero g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. V\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Caballero m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9o xa h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Caballero khi m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 The Blues qu\u00e1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh v\u00e0 Aguero th\u00ec ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn:</h2>\r\n<h2>Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh. Trong 70 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Morata t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 20 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng, 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1edd h\u1eefng c\u1ee7a Morata tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m cho Pedro c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Hudson-Odoi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Morata kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marcos Alonso\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/033433-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt SarriBall trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y m\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng th\u00ec Alonso m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. HLV Sarri r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00ean trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Emerson Palmieri \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, David Luiz l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man City tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i lao v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Luiz t\u1ef1 tin khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i va ch\u1ea1m quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luiz \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng 5 \u0103n 5 thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Luiz. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thay v\u00ec Christensen. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city-172-193811.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2037","checkdouble":"193809"},{"date":"02:30 06/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Aguero \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ecbu thua m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat kh\u00e1ng c\u1ef1 n\u00e0o.</h2><h2>Jorginho g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea thua Man City \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea thua Man City \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jorginho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Man City. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 The Blues ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Jorginho d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn Jorginho c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y The Blues v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ec5 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Jorginho ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Fabregas c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u1edf n\u00ean mong manh. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu mang t\u00ean Jorginho c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00e1p s\u00e1t ngay khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. Khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, Jorginho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n Kante quay v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rudiger\" title=\"Rudiger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antonio Rudiger v\u00e0 David Luiz l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\" target=\"_blank\">Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018</span>. V\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n trong hai b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 Chelsea ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Rudiger \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp can thi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Aguero. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Luiz khi \u0111\u1ec3 Aguero lu\u1ed3n sau l\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u0103m n\u00e1t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng nh\u00e1t dao ch\u00ed m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i th\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Aguero c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Caballero. N\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Aguero \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick ho\u1eb7c poker \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u00f9n m\u00f2n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n v\u00e0 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1eeda v\u1eddi. The Blues c\u0169ng c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n nguy hi\u1ec3m th\u1eadt s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlvaro Morata v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. Pedro m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong khi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Willian ph\u00fat 59 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0o. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Hudson-Odoi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Kyle Walker th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Odoi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ef1u chung l\u1ea1i, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri v\u00e0 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i top 4 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-chelsea-02-man-city-172-193803.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-phat-bieu-sau-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-tranh-sieu-cup-anh-2018-172-193802.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f9ng Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2036","checkdouble":"193811"},{"date":"02:37 06/08","title":"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?</h2><h2>L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean so s\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nhau. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean n\u1ebfu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 thua Uzbekistan \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f2n Palestine h\u1ea1 Oman, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eabn Palestine s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch do h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u0129nh ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 20.000 \u0111\u00f4la M\u1ef9. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a VFF, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ASIAD. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nHy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br />\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\">\u201cHi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu\u201d</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng HLV qu\u1ed1c gia, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2035","checkdouble":"193812"},{"date":"03:37 06/08","title":"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t:</h2>\r\n<h2>Sergio Aguero\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aguero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 200 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aguero ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-hom-nay-372-193779.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea vs Man City</span> v\u1eeba qua. Anh l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAguero \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Luiz &ndash; Rudiger c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Aguero. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAguero \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng Rudiger \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Luiz \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Aguero c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua David Luiz kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho HLV Pep Guardiola th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thay v\u00ec Gabriel Jesus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bernardo Silva</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Bernardo Silva sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, Silva \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &ldquo; nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng d\u00f9 l\u00e0 nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Bernardo Silva x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva s\u1ebd l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man City m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c De Bruyne v\u00e0 Sterling s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd xoay s\u1edf th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willy Caballero\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willy Caballero\" title=\"Willy Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/033503-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Willy Caballero c\u1ee9u cho Chelsea v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u00f4ng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Cheasea. Sau s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Callum Hudson-Odoi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Caballero g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. V\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Caballero m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9o xa h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Caballero khi m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 The Blues qu\u00e1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh v\u00e0 Aguero th\u00ec ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn:</h2>\r\n<h2>Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh. Trong 70 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Morata t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 20 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng, 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1edd h\u1eefng c\u1ee7a Morata tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m cho Pedro c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Hudson-Odoi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Morata kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marcos Alonso\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/033433-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt SarriBall trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y m\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng th\u00ec Alonso m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. HLV Sarri r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00ean trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Emerson Palmieri \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, David Luiz l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man City tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i lao v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Luiz t\u1ef1 tin khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i va ch\u1ea1m quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luiz \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng 5 \u0103n 5 thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Luiz. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thay v\u00ec Christensen. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city-172-193811.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2034","checkdouble":"193815"},{"date":"03:54 06/08","title":"Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri \"b\u1ea3o k\u00ea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><h2>Barkley ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barkley \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 l\u1ea7n sau khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea t\u1eeb Everton h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, Barkley l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Barkley ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen ng\u1ee3i Barkley\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barkley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barkley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barkley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-hom-nay-372-193779.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span> nh\u01b0ng HLV Sarri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Barkley v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Barkley l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Jorginho, Fabregas v\u00e0 Barkley c\u00f9ng nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Chelsea c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Huddersfield v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd ni\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u00e1p s\u00e1t. \u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00e1p s\u00e1t \u0111\u00fang, \u0111\u00f4i khi sai. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh suy ngh\u0129 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Tu\u1ea7n sau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Lyon. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nhanh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-172-193815.html\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city-172-193811.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN) </strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2033","checkdouble":"193816"},{"date":"05:33 06/08","title":"Pep Guardiola ch\u1ec9 ra hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-pep-guardiola-phat-bieu-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ca ng\u1ee3i Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-khen-ngoi-Sergio-Aguero-va-Bernardo-Silva-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva sau khi Man City th\u1eafng Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Aguero th\u00ec hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Chelsea \u1edf Wembley, mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa cho Man City. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup. Kun lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Ramon Cugat l\u00e0 b\u00e1c s\u0129 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u00ec gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n. H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 3-4-5 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i hay nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola ch\u1ec9 ra hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ch\u1ec9 ra hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hlv-pep-guardiola-phat-bieu-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernardo Silva thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf\u00a0tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i ca m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u1edf Etihad, gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u00ecnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia x\u1ee9 Catalonia: \u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Bernardo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t t\u00e1c. Ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Bernardo \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 David Silva \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u00eam t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean tr\u00ean cao nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o. Bernardo th\u00f4ng minh tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tinh th\u1ea7n, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Man City xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do, v\u00e0 Bernardo ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-Chelsea-vs-Man-City.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2032","checkdouble":"193821"},{"date":"06:19 06/08","title":"MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ecb n\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mua s\u1eafm.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd k\u1ebft th\u00fac chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 bu\u1ed3n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n vui c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193792.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bayern Munich</span>. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho g\u1eedi t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho BL\u0110 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho g\u1eedi t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho BL\u0110 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jose\u00a0Mourinho \u0111ang b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 v\u00ec k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, MU m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ba t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 gi\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Lee Grant v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Diogo Dalot c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn sang c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch hay top 4 Premier League, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng duy\u1ec7t chi cho 3/4 qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u cho m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern Munich 1-0 MU ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 g\u1eedi g\u1eafm gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNg\u00e0i CEO bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec v\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00edt ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i xem m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 gi\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 Liverpool, b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111ang mua h\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0o h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 n\u0103m 9/8 trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u cho Man Utd h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ch\u00f3t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>Video Bayern Munich 1-0 MU:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/hx3zEr.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2031","checkdouble":"193823"},{"date":"05:58 06/08","title":"N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd k\u1ebft th\u00fac chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 bu\u1ed3n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n vui c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193792.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bayern Munich</span>. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a BL\u0110.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi MU trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Marcus Rashford ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp b\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebf th\u1eeba nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 David Beckham, Teddy Sheringham, Ruud Van Nistelrooy, Wayne Rooney v\u00e0 Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh qua ba n\u0103m kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf Old Trafford, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng \u00e1o l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eeb 39 xu\u1ed1ng 19 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 10.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Rashford \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Mourinho ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Man Utd m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng hay v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Rashford, r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 h\u00fat c\u1ea1n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3 h\u1ebft m\u1ef1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y sao cho x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 mang tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 10 Rashford s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, khi Man Utd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u0129nh \u1ea5n khai h\u1ed9i Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ngh\u00eanh \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ru\u1ed9t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 20.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Video tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich 1-0 MU:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/hx3zEr.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2030","checkdouble":"193824"},{"date":"14:24 05/08","title":"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Maguire v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/bom-tan-maguire-van-co-the-duoc-mu-kich-no-o-he-2018.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Co-hoi-de-MU-Harry-Maguire-cua-Leicester-la-van-con-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leicester ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Maguire\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho M.U, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, Maguire s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/leicester-lam-dieu-nay-de-giu-chan-harry-maguire-172-192395.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leicester mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Maguire</span>. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 (t\u1eeb 50.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n l\u00ean 95.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Maguire qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n Yerry Mina \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Co-hoi-de-MU-Harry-Maguire-cua-Leicester-la-van-con-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, Maguire l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1ea5t. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo cho Everton \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Mourinho v\u1eabn \u01b0u ti\u00ean Maguire, ch\u1ec9 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2029","checkdouble":"193770"},{"date":"14:53 05/08","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Iniesta, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Pogba trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sport, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ri\u00eang Pogba, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/cuc-nong-pogba-da-chon-xong-so-ao-o-barca-180-193721.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf Barca</span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o do huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" title=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/20/andy-cole-khong-danh-gia-cao-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf cho ph\u00e9p. Theo t\u1edd Daily Star, Mino Raiola s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ph\u00eda M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Barcelona ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i, Pogba s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2028","checkdouble":"193771"},{"date":"15:59 05/08","title":"Real Madrid nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 200 tri\u1ec7u euro thay Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinaphone 2018 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Oman l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP OLYMPIC VI\u1ec6T NAM VS OLYMPIC OMAN</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DgL2cBwfQ7s\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,\u2026 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay hay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai \u0111i, ai \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SLNA, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ecfng \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea5u Oman, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Truc-tiep-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-ngay-hom-nay,-link-xem-HD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a hai n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110TQG) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p \u0110TQG Oman \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 14 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Do \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh.<br>\r\nU23 Oman: Mukhaini; Harthi, Rashi Al, Shayadi, Sulaman Al, Balushi, Mubarak Al, Saleh Al, Al Hidi, Ali Al, Al Sabhi.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2027","checkdouble":"193772"},{"date":"15:59 05/08","title":"Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d MU l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian cho Barca, song h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb M.U. Mourinho \u0111ang th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Chelsea-muon-mua-Wilfried-Zaha-thay-Willian-voi-gia-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri t\u1ecf ra t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng Chelsea do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi \u0111\u1ee7 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Theo Daily Mail, M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i cho Willian, theo \u0111\u00f3 Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Zaha l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/zaha-moi-goi-chelsea-172-192605.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea</span>, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, HLV Roy Hodgson tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Palace kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Zaha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea muon mua Zaha voi gia 75 trieu bang\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Man City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ef1u sao M.U, song Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c Man xanh ph\u1ea3i chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester. N\u1ebfu Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Zaha, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Mirror, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Willian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2026","checkdouble":"193773"},{"date":"15:01 05/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 05/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0508.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 05/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0508-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m. Mina s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, t\u1ee9c x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 145.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc thu\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Valverde t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-pogba-180-193728.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/12/MU-ap-dao-doi-hinh-te-nhat-vong-9-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-pogba-180-193728.html\">HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?</span><br>\r\nErnesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan t\u00ednh v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u00e0 Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Maguire v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea7ng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Man United, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire hay Yerry Mina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ivan Perisic mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0508-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian-172-193732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian-172-193732.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</span><br>\r\nBenfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Martial\" title=\"tien dao Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-38,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mua Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu-172-192610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu-172-192610.html\">Tottenham nh\u1eafn MU: 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng = Alderweireld + Rose</span><br>\r\nTottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo CalcioMarceto, Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o do huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2025","checkdouble":"193774"}]}